### ============================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN
### ============================================

### 1. Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ivan@planazo.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Ivan"
}

### 2. Login (copia el token de la respuesta)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ivan@planazo.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Verificar token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ============================================
### GESTIÓN DE PERFIL (requiere token)
### ============================================

### 4. Ver mi perfil
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 5. Actualizar mi perfil
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nombre": "Ivan Actualizado",
  "bio": "Desarrollador fullstack apasionado por crear apps increíbles",
  "fotoUrl": "https://ejemplo.com/mi-foto.jpg"
}

### 6. Ver perfil de otro usuario (cambia el ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 7. Eliminar mi cuenta (CUIDADO - esto desactiva la cuenta)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI
